uest at Paris Hotel \n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Ferdinand (film)|Ferdinand]]''\n| Picador<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cinemablend.com/news/1543510/why-paul-feig-wont-direct-any-more-remakes|title=Why Paul Feig Won't Direct Any More Remakes|accessdate=August 17, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/02/ferdinand-blue-sky-december-schedule-change-1201907181|title=Blue Sky\u2019s Bull Toon \u2018Ferdinand\u2019 To Lock Horns With \u2018Star Wars: The Last Jedi\u2019|date=February 9, 2017|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|publisher =[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=August 17, 2017}}</ref>\n| Voice role\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Song of Back and Neck]]''\n| Dr. Street\n| \n|}\n\n===Television===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" \n|-\n! Year \n! Title\n!width=65 | Director \n!width=65 | Producer \n!width=65 | Writer \n! Notes\n|-\n| 1999\n| ''[[Freaks and Geeks]]''\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| Creator;<br>Directed \"Discos and Dragons\"\n|-\n| 2005\u20132011\n| ''[[The Office (U.S. TV series)|The Office]]''\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes|Executive}}\n| \n| Episodes directed:\n*\"[[Office Olympics]]\"\n*\"[[Halloween (The Office)|Halloween]]\"\n*\"[[Performance Review]]\"\n*\"[[E-mail Surveillance]]\"\n*\"[[Survivor Man]]\"\n*\"[[Dinner Party (The Office)|Dinner Party]]\"\n*\"[[Goodbye, Toby]]\"\n*\"[[Weight Loss (The Office)|Weight Loss]]\"\n*\"[[The Surplus]]\"\n*\"[[Moroccan Christmas]]\"\n*\"[[New Boss]]\"\n*\"[[Dream Team (The Office)|Dream Team]]\"\n*\"[[Niagara (The Office)|Niagara]]\"\n*\"[[Goodbye, Michael]]\"\n|-\n| 2004\u20132005\n| ''[[Arrested Development (TV series)|Arrested Development]]''\n| {{yes}}\n| \n| \n| Episodes:\n*\"[[Whistler's Mother (Arrested Development)|Whistler's Mother]]\"\n*\"[[Let 'Em Eat Cake (Arrested Development)|Let 'Em Eat Cake]]\"\n*\"[[Switch Hitter]]\"\n*\"[[Burning Love (Arrested Development)|Burning Love]]\"\n*\"[[Ready, Aim, Marry Me]]\"\n*\"[[The Cabin Show]]\"\n*\"[[The Ocean Walker]]\"\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[Mad Men]]'' \n| {{yes}}\